name: Agog 20 Lure Sphere
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculptural sphere with texture from video art work Lure. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
